QuestData.Title: WANTED: Lady Narjiss
QuestData.Description:
Wanted for attacks against the Horde!
Lady Narjiss is responsible for leading several raids and ambushes against our soldiers.
Last seen on the outskirts of Zanj'ir Terrace. Extreme caution advised!
Upon completion of the mission, report to Seacaller Unow for commendation.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve the head of Lady Narjiss.
